<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Dhruva Wealth OS — Agent Architecture & Execution</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

:root {
–gold: #B8973A;
–gold-light: #D4AF6A;
–gold-pale: rgba(184,151,58,0.08);
–obsidian: #080809;
–charcoal: #111114;
–graphite: #18181D;
–panel: #1C1C22;
–border: rgba(184,151,58,0.12);
–border-dim: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
–mist: #7878888;
–smoke: #606070;
–ivory: #EDE8DE;
–white: #F8F6F0;
–teal: #3DC9C0;
–rose: #E07878;
–amber: #F0C040;
–blue: #5890D8;
–green: #58B878;
–mono: ‘JetBrains Mono’, monospace;
–serif: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif;
–sans: ‘Outfit’, sans-serif;
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
background: var(–obsidian);
color: var(–ivory);
font-family: var(–mono);
font-size: 12px;
line-height: 1.6;
min-height: 100vh;
}

/* GRAIN */
body::before {
content: ‘’;
position: fixed; inset: 0;
background-image: url(“data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox=‘0 0 200 200’ xmlns=‘http://www.w3.org/2000/svg’%3E%3Cfilter id=‘n’%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=‘fractalNoise’ baseFrequency=‘0.85’ numOctaves=‘4’/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=‘100%25’ height=‘100%25’ filter=‘url(%23n)’ opacity=‘0.035’/%3E%3C/svg%3E”);
pointer-events: none; z-index: 999; opacity: 0.7;
}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav {
position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
background: rgba(8,8,9,0.95);
backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
border-bottom: 1px solid var(–border);
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0;
padding: 0 40px;
overflow-x: auto;
}

.nav-brand {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: 16px;
color: var(–gold);
padding: 16px 0;
margin-right: 32px;
white-space: nowrap;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.nav-tab {
padding: 16px 20px;
font-size: 10px;
letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: #606070;
cursor: pointer;
border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
transition: all 0.2s;
white-space: nowrap;
flex-shrink: 0;
user-select: none;
}

.nav-tab:hover { color: var(–ivory); }
.nav-tab.active {
color: var(–gold);
border-bottom-color: var(–gold);
}

/* ── SECTIONS ── */
.section { display: none; padding: 48px 40px 80px; }
.section.active { display: block; }

/* ── HEADER ── */
.page-header {
margin-bottom: 40px;
padding-bottom: 32px;
border-bottom: 1px solid var(–border);
}

.eyebrow {
font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 4px;
text-transform: uppercase; color: var(–gold);
margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.page-header h1 {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
font-weight: 300; color: var(–white);
line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.page-header h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(–gold-light); }

.page-header p {
font-size: 12px; color: #606070;
max-width: 700px; line-height: 1.8;
}

/* ── TCF BANNER ── */
.tcf-banner {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
gap: 1px;
background: var(–border);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.tcf-cell {
background: var(–charcoal);
padding: 24px 28px;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
}

.tcf-cell::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
height: 2px;
}
.tcf-cell.t::before { background: var(–blue); }
.tcf-cell.c::before { background: var(–amber); }
.tcf-cell.d::before { background: var(–green); }

.tcf-num {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: 40px; font-weight: 300;
line-height: 1;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.tcf-cell.t .tcf-num { color: rgba(88,144,216,0.2); }
.tcf-cell.c .tcf-num { color: rgba(240,192,64,0.2); }
.tcf-cell.d .tcf-num { color: rgba(88,184,120,0.2); }

.tcf-label {
font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px;
text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;
}
.tcf-cell.t .tcf-label { color: var(–blue); }
.tcf-cell.c .tcf-label { color: var(–amber); }
.tcf-cell.d .tcf-label { color: var(–green); }

.tcf-desc {
font-size: 11px; color: #606070;
margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.6;
}

.tcf-arrow {
position: absolute; right: 16px; top: 50%;
transform: translateY(-50%);
font-size: 20px; color: var(–border);
font-family: var(–mono);
}

/* ── ORG CHART ── */
.org-wrap {
overflow-x: auto;
padding-bottom: 16px;
margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.org-chart {
min-width: 800px;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
gap: 0;
}

.org-level {
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
gap: 0;
position: relative;
width: 100%;
}

.org-node {
background: var(–panel);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
padding: 16px 20px;
text-align: center;
position: relative;
min-width: 160px;
max-width: 200px;
transition: all 0.2s;
}

.org-node:hover {
background: var(–graphite);
border-color: rgba(184,151,58,0.4);
}

.org-node.principal {
border-color: var(–gold);
background: rgba(184,151,58,0.08);
min-width: 200px;
}

.org-node.cto { border-top: 3px solid var(–teal); }
.org-node.cio { border-top: 3px solid var(–amber); }
.org-node.dev { border-top: 3px solid rgba(88,205,192,0.4); }
.org-node.qa  { border-top: 3px solid rgba(88,205,192,0.3); }
.org-node.content  { border-top: 3px solid rgba(240,192,64,0.4); }
.org-node.outreach { border-top: 3px solid rgba(240,192,64,0.3); }

.node-role {
font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase; color: #606070;
margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.node-title {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: 16px; color: var(–white);
margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.node-model {
font-size: 9px; color: var(–gold);
letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.node-focus {
font-size: 9px; color: #505060;
margin-top: 6px; line-height: 1.5;
}

/* connector lines */
.connector-v {
width: 1px;
background: var(–border);
margin: 0 auto;
height: 32px;
}

.connector-h-wrap {
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
position: relative;
width: 100%;
height: 32px;
}

.connector-h {
position: absolute;
top: 0;
height: 1px;
background: var(–border);
}

.connector-down-left, .connector-down-right {
position: absolute;
width: 1px;
top: 0; bottom: 0;
background: var(–border);
}

.org-sub-group {
display: flex;
gap: 1px;
background: var(–border);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
}

/* ── WORKFLOW DIAGRAM ── */
.workflow {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
gap: 2px;
margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.wf-lane {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
gap: 1px;
background: var(–border-dim);
border: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
min-height: 80px;
}

.wf-label {
background: var(–charcoal);
padding: 16px;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
justify-content: center;
border-right: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
}

.wf-lane-name {
font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;
}

.wf-lane.traffic .wf-lane-name   { color: var(–blue); }
.wf-lane.convert .wf-lane-name   { color: var(–amber); }
.wf-lane.deliver .wf-lane-name   { color: var(–green); }
.wf-lane.infra .wf-lane-name     { color: #606070; }

.wf-body {
background: var(–charcoal);
padding: 16px 20px;
display: flex;
flex-wrap: wrap;
gap: 8px;
align-items: center;
}

.wf-step {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 8px;
}

.wf-box {
padding: 6px 12px;
border: 1px solid;
font-size: 10px;
white-space: nowrap;
letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.wf-lane.traffic .wf-box  { border-color: rgba(88,144,216,0.3); color: var(–blue); background: rgba(88,144,216,0.05); }
.wf-lane.convert .wf-box  { border-color: rgba(240,192,64,0.3); color: var(–amber); background: rgba(240,192,64,0.05); }
.wf-lane.deliver .wf-box  { border-color: rgba(88,184,120,0.3); color: var(–green); background: rgba(88,184,120,0.05); }
.wf-lane.infra .wf-box    { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #606070; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }

.wf-arrow { color: #404050; font-size: 14px; }

/* ── SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE ── */
.arch-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
gap: 1px;
background: var(–border-dim);
border: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.arch-layer {
background: var(–charcoal);
padding: 24px;
}

.arch-layer-title {
font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 4px;
text-transform: uppercase; color: var(–gold);
margin-bottom: 16px;
padding-bottom: 12px;
border-bottom: 1px solid var(–border);
}

.arch-item {
display: flex;
gap: 10px;
margin-bottom: 10px;
align-items: flex-start;
}

.arch-dot {
width: 6px; height: 6px;
border-radius: 50%;
margin-top: 5px;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.arch-item-text {
font-size: 11px;
line-height: 1.5;
}

.arch-item-name {
color: var(–ivory);
display: block;
font-weight: 500;
}

.arch-item-sub {
color: #505060;
display: block;
font-size: 10px;
}

/* ── AGENT CARDS ── */
.agent-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
gap: 1px;
background: var(–border);
border: 1px solid var(–border);
margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.agent-card {
background: var(–charcoal);
padding: 28px 32px;
position: relative;
}

.agent-card::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
height: 3px;
}

.agent-card.cto::before { background: var(–teal); }
.agent-card.cio::before { background: var(–amber); }
.agent-card.dev::before { background: rgba(88,205,192,0.5); }
.agent-card.qa::before  { background: rgba(88,205,192,0.3); }
.agent-card.content::before  { background: rgba(240,192,64,0.5); }
.agent-card.outreach::before { background: rgba(240,192,64,0.3); }

.agent-header {
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
align-items: flex-start;
margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.agent-title {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: 22px; color: var(–white);
margin-bottom: 2px;
}

.agent-subtitle {
font-size: 10px; color: #606070;
letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.model-tag {
padding: 4px 10px;
border: 1px solid var(–border);
font-size: 9px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
color: var(–gold);
white-space: nowrap;
}

.agent-section {
margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.agent-section-label {
font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase; color: #505060;
margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.agent-section.t .agent-section-label { color: rgba(88,144,216,0.7); }
.agent-section.c .agent-section-label { color: rgba(240,192,64,0.7); }
.agent-section.d .agent-section-label { color: rgba(88,184,120,0.7); }

.tag-list {
display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px;
}

.tag {
padding: 3px 8px;
font-size: 10px;
letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.tag-t { border: 1px solid rgba(88,144,216,0.2); color: rgba(88,144,216,0.8); background: rgba(88,144,216,0.04); }
.tag-c { border: 1px solid rgba(240,192,64,0.2); color: rgba(240,192,64,0.8); background: rgba(240,192,64,0.04); }
.tag-d { border: 1px solid rgba(88,184,120,0.2); color: rgba(88,184,120,0.8); background: rgba(88,184,120,0.04); }
.tag-x { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: #505060; }

.prompt-box {
background: var(–graphite);
border: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
border-left: 2px solid var(–gold);
padding: 14px 16px;
font-size: 10px;
color: #808090;
line-height: 1.7;
font-style: italic;
margin-top: 8px;
}

.prompt-box strong { color: var(–ivory); font-style: normal; }

/* ── MCP TASKS ── */
.mcp-section {
margin-bottom: 40px;
border: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
}

.mcp-header {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr auto;
align-items: center;
gap: 0;
background: var(–panel);
border-bottom: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
padding: 0;
}

.mcp-id {
padding: 16px;
font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px;
color: var(–gold);
border-right: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
font-weight: 600;
}

.mcp-title-wrap {
padding: 16px 20px;
}

.mcp-title {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: 18px; color: var(–white);
}

.mcp-subtitle {
font-size: 10px; color: #505060;
margin-top: 2px;
}

.mcp-meta {
padding: 16px;
text-align: right;
border-left: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
min-width: 130px;
}

.mcp-quarter {
font-size: 10px; color: var(–gold-light);
margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.mcp-owner {
font-size: 9px; color: #505060;
letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.mcp-body {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
gap: 1px;
background: var(–border-dim);
}

.mcp-col {
background: var(–charcoal);
padding: 20px;
}

.mcp-col-title {
font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;
padding-bottom: 10px;
border-bottom: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
}

.mcp-col.t .mcp-col-title { color: var(–blue); }
.mcp-col.c .mcp-col-title { color: var(–amber); }
.mcp-col.d .mcp-col-title { color: var(–green); }

.task-item {
display: flex; gap: 8px;
margin-bottom: 10px;
align-items: flex-start;
}

.task-num {
font-size: 9px; color: var(–gold);
flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;
font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px;
min-width: 20px;
}

.task-text {
font-size: 11px; color: #808090;
line-height: 1.5;
}

.task-text strong { color: var(–ivory); font-weight: 500; }
.task-text code {
font-size: 10px; color: var(–teal);
background: rgba(61,201,192,0.06);
padding: 1px 4px;
}

/* ── PAPERCLIP GUIDE ── */
.step-block {
margin-bottom: 32px;
border: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
}

.step-header {
display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0;
background: var(–panel);
border-bottom: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
}

.step-num-box {
padding: 16px 20px;
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300;
color: rgba(184,151,58,0.3);
border-right: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
min-width: 64px;
text-align: center;
}

.step-title-wrap {
padding: 14px 20px;
}

.step-title {
font-family: var(–serif);
font-size: 18px; color: var(–white);
}

.step-subtitle {
font-size: 10px; color: #505060;
margin-top: 2px; letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.step-agent-badge {
margin-left: auto;
padding: 6px 16px;
font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px;
text-transform: uppercase;
margin-right: 16px;
}

.badge-cto { border: 1px solid rgba(61,201,192,0.3); color: var(–teal); }
.badge-cio { border: 1px solid rgba(240,192,64,0.3); color: var(–amber); }
.badge-all { border: 1px solid var(–border); color: #606070; }

.step-body {
padding: 24px;
background: var(–charcoal);
}

.step-instructions {
display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;
margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.instruction {
display: flex; gap: 12px;
align-items: flex-start;
}

.ins-marker {
font-size: 9px; color: var(–gold);
flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 3px;
font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px;
min-width: 32px;
}

.ins-text {
font-size: 12px; color: #909090;
line-height: 1.6;
}

.ins-text strong { color: var(–ivory); font-weight: 500; }
.ins-text code {
font-size: 11px; color: var(–teal);
background: rgba(61,201,192,0.06);
padding: 2px 6px;
display: inline-block;
}

.code-block {
background: #0D0D10;
border: 1px solid rgba(61,201,192,0.15);
border-left: 3px solid var(–teal);
padding: 16px 20px;
font-size: 11px;
color: #80C0B8;
line-height: 1.8;
margin-top: 16px;
white-space: pre-wrap;
overflow-x: auto;
}

.code-block .comment { color: #404858; }
.code-block .key { color: var(–gold-light); }
.code-block .val { color: var(–teal); }
.code-block .str { color: #90C890; }

.callout {
display: flex; gap: 12px;
padding: 14px 18px;
border-left: 2px solid var(–gold);
background: var(–gold-pale);
margin-top: 16px;
align-items: flex-start;
}

.callout-icon { color: var(–gold); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
.callout-text { font-size: 11px; color: var(–ivory); line-height: 1.6; }
.callout-text strong { color: var(–gold-light); }

/* ── SUMMARY TABLE ── */
.summary-table {
width: 100%;
border-collapse: collapse;
border: 1px solid var(–border);
margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.summary-table th {
background: var(–obsidian);
padding: 10px 14px;
text-align: left;
font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px;
color: #505060; text-transform: uppercase;
font-weight: 400;
border-bottom: 1px solid var(–border);
}

.summary-table td {
padding: 12px 14px;
border-bottom: 1px solid var(–border-dim);
font-size: 11px; color: #808090;
vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.5;
}

.summary-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.summary-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015); }

.td-name { color: var(–ivory) !important; font-weight: 500; }
.td-done { color: var(–green) !important; }
.td-q1 { color: var(–gold-light) !important; }
.td-q2 { color: var(–amber) !important; }
.td-q3 { color: var(–blue) !important; }
.td-q4 { color: var(–rose) !important; }

/* ── STATUS DOT ── */
.dot { display: inline-block; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: middle; }
.dot-done { background: var(–green); }
.dot-q1   { background: var(–gold); }
.dot-q2   { background: var(–amber); }
.dot-q3   { background: var(–blue); }
.dot-q4   { background: var(–rose); }

/* SCROLLBAR */
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 3px; height: 3px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(–obsidian); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(184,151,58,0.25); }

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
nav { padding: 0 16px; }
.section { padding: 32px 16px 60px; }
.tcf-banner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
.agent-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
.mcp-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
.arch-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
.org-chart { min-width: 600px; }
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<!-- ══ NAV ══ -->

<nav>
  <div class="nav-brand">Dhruva ✦</div>
  <div class="nav-tab active" onclick="show('arch')">Architecture</div>
  <div class="nav-tab" onclick="show('agents')">Agent Configs</div>
  <div class="nav-tab" onclick="show('tasks')">Technical Tasks</div>
  <div class="nav-tab" onclick="show('paperclip')">Paperclip Setup</div>
</nav>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════ TAB 1: ARCHITECTURE ══ -->

<section id="arch" class="section active">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="eyebrow">Dhruva Wealth OS — Agent Architecture</div>
    <h1>System Design &amp;<br><em>Execution Blueprint</em></h1>
    <p>Traffic → Conversion → Delivery framework applied to a lean 6-agent Paperclip network. CTO owns technical execution. CIO owns commercial execution. You own direction and client relationships.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- TCF BANNER -->

  <div class="tcf-banner">
    <div class="tcf-cell t">
      <div class="tcf-num">01</div>
      <div class="tcf-label">Traffic</div>
      <div class="tcf-desc">People discovering Dhruva. LinkedIn content, BAPS network, accounting communities, conference presence. CIO + Content Agent own this lane.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tcf-cell c">
